inary", "id": "6777997792324771"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "247209914665124"}]}, "change_log": "v.1.1.1.1\nFixed an issue where the weapon sometimes failed to shoot as expected\nFixed performance issues in the friends interface that could lead to lag or even crashes\nFixed the RC416\u2019s inability to properly equip a muzzle compensator\nFixed lag issues on the Outlaw Den map", "created_date": 1724323054, "id": "6704922762965608", "version": "1.0", "version_code": 144, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "6704900259634525"}, "asset_files": {"count": 3}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "4963431797114722", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "6777997792324771"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "247209914665124"}]}, "change_log": "v.1.1.1.0\nAdded new circle areas in Reborn mode\nImproved server performance\nAttempted to fix issues with ground items being difficult to pick up\nAttempted to fix the issue where teammates in the ARK PIT did not have team markers\nFixed the issue where teammate sound effects could be heard\nAttempted to fix possible server crash issues\nAdjusted display settings for Quest 3\nAttempted to fix the issue where weapons might automatically stop firing\nFixed abnormal installation of tactical items with MICA\nAttempted to fix the issue where UI elements of other players could be seen in Reborn mode\nAttempted to fix the issue with teammate models loading incorrectly\nAttempted to fix the issue where the escort mission UI did not remove correctly\nFixed the issue where items were not received correctly after purchasing insurance and reviving\nAttempted to fix item anomalies after reviving in Reborn mode\nFixed the issue where backpack expansion sometimes failed\nFixed the issue where it was difficult to retrieve weapons from the left shoulder after weapon mirroring\nFixed the issue where DBP12 gunstock calibration was ineffective and added gunstock calibration for MP5A3 and PKP\nFixed the issue where aiming with the Savior scope could cause the weapon position to be abnormal\nFixed the issue where Flame12's gunfire sound would cut off when hitting targets continuously\nFixed the issue where Fury V skin: Astral could easily hit the user while moving forward\nOptimized the reload trigger range for AKS74U\nOptimized the issue where magazines could immediately return to the backpack when quickly drawn out during fast movements such as in the air or while driving\nOptimized the issue where PKP did not correctly enter the aiming state when using a 4x dot\nFixed the issue where the OCP-7 scope was sometimes unclear\nFixed the collision issue preventing exit from the rooftop attic of some buildings in New City\nFixed the collision issue on the stairs of the corridor near the airport leading to the cave\nFixed the issue where some models on the north side of New Town Street had dark lighting\nFixed the collision issue in Black Market Canyon where there was a seam between the cliff and the terrain that people could get into\nFixed the collision issue with the metal plate on the platform on the south side of the Factory's large workshop\nFixed the issue where the sea surface at HQ disappeared\nFixed the seam issues with some window frames in New Town buildings\nFixed the seam issues with some door frames in Airport buildings\nFixed the issue where fences in farmland suddenly appeared\nFixed the issue with some dirt road models being dark", "created_date": 1722611299, "id": "6595270860597466", "version": "1.0", "version_code": 143, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "bin